These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, baccarat
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, teacher
1. the mechanic is in an even position##4
2. the teacher is the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Cigar   | baccarat | old-henry |
| Job     | teacher    | mechanic   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: orchid, balloon-flower
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Flower   | balloon-flower | orchid        |
| Sport      | sailing  | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, house
City: venice, nizza
1. the person traveling to venice is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | house    | ambient |
| City   | venice | nizza |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  paramedic, manager
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, mango
1. the manager is on the right of the paramedic##1
2. the person eating mango is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Job   | paramedic      | manager |
| Food       | broccoli | mango    |

