.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-11::.
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, polish
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, scientific
1. the polish is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the canadian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Nationality   | polish | canadian   |
| Movie-Genre         | zombie | scientific |

