.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-12::.
2 different games are played: bridge, monopoly
There are 2 different nationalities: british, indonesian
1. the british is the person playing bridge##1
2. the indonesian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Game   | monopoly       | bridge   |
| Nationality   | indonesian | british |

