.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-18::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, december
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, weightlifting
1. the person who's birthday is in november is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |
| Birthday    | november | december       |
| Sport   | water-polo  | weightlifting |

