.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, lemonade
2 different pets are kept: goat, turtle
1. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | tea | lemonade  |
| Pet   | goat      | turtle |

 